= SDL_UnlockTexture =
Use this function to unlock a texture, uploading the changes to video memory, if needed.


== Syntax ==
```c++
void SDL_UnlockTexture(SDL_TextureID textureID)
```

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''textureID'''
|the texture locked by [[SDL_LockTexture]]() that is to be unlocked
|}

